						<div class="postbody">Are you willing to post a ROM?<br /><br />Nintendulator has a reputation for getting these things correct, so I would tend to suspect FCEUX is in error (though obviously we should verify).<br /><br />If there is a bug in FCEUX I'd recommend reporting it here: <a href="http://sourceforge.net/p/fceultra/bugs/" class="postlink">http://sourceforge.net/p/fceultra/bugs/</a><br /><br />Have you tried switching FCEUX from Old PPU mode to New PPU mode? (Config menu &gt; PPU.)<br /><br />I've seen FCEUX do lots of splits correctly, but maybe you've exposed a new problem for it. There is probably an alternative way to do what you're doing that is robust enough to work with FCEUX regardless.</div>

