				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">FCEUX is crazy aggressive about simulating bus conflicts.  Make sure you aren't encountering any of those when you bankswitch.  Or in other words, make sure the byte in ROM you are writing to has the exact same value as what you're writing.</div>

					
